OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778497375
OL,3,CServices commemorate fishermen lost at
OL,4,Csea
OL,6,FFor coastal communities across the UK,
OL,7,Fthe day serves as a focal point for
OL,8,Fremembrance and connection with the
OL,9,Ffishing industry.
OL,11,FServices took place in Weymouth,
OL,12,FPortsmouth, Newbury, Hastings and
OL,13,FNewhaven.
OL,15,FAround 11,000 people working in
OL,16,Fchallenging and unpredictable
OL,17,Fconditions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
