CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778497375
OL,3,CServices commemorate fishermen lost at
OL,4,Csea
OL,6,FMany harbours have experienced
OL,7,Ftragedy, and this day recognises those
OL,8,Flosses while reinforcing the
OL,9,Fimportance of improving safety
OL,10,Fstandards, working practices, and
OL,11,Fsupport for crews and their families.
OL,13,FOne of the most significant recent
OL,14,Ffishing tragedies in Weymouth occurred
OL,15,Fin 2012 when the Purbeck Isle sank off
OL,16,FPortland Bill, resulting in the loss
OL,17,Fof three lives.
OL,19,FA malfunctioning life raft was the
OL,20,Fcause.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
